{"tid":47285,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇HR 或熟勞工法例巴絲幫幫手","createTime":"2016-12-20T08:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T13:28:37.000Z","uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99adc6bedb4192ed35a9587dc7d28e33e48f1217","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"小弟做緊PART TIME<br />\n9月尾開始返 到依家<br />\n因為僱主過度苛刻(e.g. sick leave 有醫生紙都請唔到）<br />\n所以想resign<br />\n琴日放工同老細講話resign<br />\n佢話要一個月通知<br />\n<br />\n我返屋企睇contract 完全冇提及resign細節<br />\n所以同返佢講話contract 冇寫 即日reaign<br />\n我諗個老細之後應該刨過下份contract<br />\n<br />\n佢今朝wtsapp 我話我毀約，內容：<br />\n<br />\nIn carrying out these duties and responsibilities, the Employee shall comply with all Employer policies, procedures, rules and regulations, both written and oral, as are announced by the Employer from time to time.<br />\n<br />\n巴絲可唔可以幫手睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d312cbbd254c6378e5004e44fbac7a1b3ae6f5","tid":47285,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"冇寫就跟返勞工法例"},{"pid":"e5c2520b28cda830875e8a8525c7ca43ebb4781c","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇寫就跟返勞工法例</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks 巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依家話 一個月通知係 佢口頭講 所以要跟<br />\n但依樣野佢未提過<br />\n係我resign 後先講<br />\n我係唔係唔算毀約？"},{"pid":"fa6d5d22f8e5107025fa47b0f3da39958b0acb08","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"希望巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> y"},{"pid":"d78732479aabb146ae25260c9f71b1fb84dc8ba4","tid":47285,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"無寫就跟勞工法，咁如果無試用期就應該係一個月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57d_whole.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57d_whole.htm&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1Ln8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=fd669a34\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57d_whole.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW，其實法例有講每個月至少有兩日病假，咁當然，病假係可以無薪。"},{"pid":"92b026ffd8726f89217f35c2ab31f3df2be92655","tid":47285,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"過左試用期一個月通知"},{"pid":"4b10e2238c312f04eefd4aeb3ac07774a65f241c","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"我未過試用期，但返左接近三個月<br />\n係唔係要7日通知？<br />\n<br />\n勞工法例上 受僱主苛待 包括d 咩？<br />\nsick leave 有醫生紙都請唔到算唔算？"},{"pid":"c01283f928fd2cd226013b767cec6f94e1f43059","tid":47285,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟做緊PART TIME<br />\n9月尾開始返 到依家<br />\n因為僱主過度苛刻(e.g. sick leave 有醫生紙都請唔到）<br />\n所以想resign<br />\n琴日放工同老細講話resign<br />\n佢話要一個月通知<br />\n<br />\n我返屋企睇contract 完全冇提及resign細節<br />\n所以同返佢講話contract 冇寫 即日reaign<br />\n我諗個老細之後應該刨過下份contract<br />\n<br />\n佢今朝wtsapp 我話我毀約，內容：<br />\n<br />\nIn carrying out these duties and responsibilities, the Employee shall comply with all Employer policies, procedures, rules and regulations, both written and oral, as are announced by the Employer from time to time.<br />\n<br />\n巴絲可唔可以幫手睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無寫就按法例<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/172443_1b49b1def8e9b094e3033a078d522d9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F172443_1b49b1def8e9b094e3033a078d522d9f.jpg&h=b86be8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要留意返你contract有無寫試用期幾耐，同埋過左試用期未<br />\n<br />\n有病假紙一定要畀你放病假，但病假唔夠連續4日可以唔畀錢"},{"pid":"885fa7de5df548a51d06907fb7e7e7566e088601","tid":47285,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"part time 要通知架咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8689cf6c0a90169019504818954dc3cd45680b2d","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>part time 要通知架咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係第一次聽<br />\n個老細明玩野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06675f26b988214c0f522a8e79d08b43192c895","tid":47285,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"應該可以去勞工處問？"},{"pid":"593535570fb6ba763012063eb28f55662a01b16a","tid":47285,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:34:01.000Z","msg":"btw 岩岩上網幫你睇過 聽上面班巴打就ok<br />\n合約無寫 口頭上又無講咩野試用期既話<br />\n<br />\n就跟番法例做番足俾佢 1個月通知"},{"pid":"d4b70f5fe1428fc3562f292111ca59b8b0929d63","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 岩岩上網幫你睇過 聽上面班巴打就ok<br />\n合約無寫 口頭上又無講咩野試用期既話<br />\n<br />\n就跟番法例做番足俾佢 1個月通知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果我話返多一個月<br />\n但依個月全部請假 可唔可行？"},{"pid":"dc32a272ee02d931276ed058c9f8dde5dc8153c1","tid":47285,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"樓上張圖唔該收一收皮<br />\n寫到明係「連續性合約」<br />\nPT唔係 所以先有418既存在"},{"pid":"bbb5dbb01b362dc2bb26403a1cd024ddffc76abe","tid":47285,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>part time 要通知架咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係第一次聽<br />\n個老細明玩野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\npart time 唔係話走就走架咩？"},{"pid":"b9574970c77fb2a865dbfaf09957b09e4b5645fa","tid":47285,"uid":41997,"like":0,"disli